---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Lánc-kezelés — Több autókozmetika egy adminban | BoxBook"
  description="2+ telephelyes autókozmetika-láncoknak: közös admin, lánc-szintű hűségpont és bérlet, központi vendég-bázis, szalon-szintű árazás. Per szalon 9 900 Ft / hó."
  canonical="/lanc"
>
  <section id="lanc" class="relative">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 lg:px-8 py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-end mb-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 fade-up">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full grad-bg text-ink-900 px-3 py-1 text-[11px] font-extrabold tracking-widest uppercase">Lánc-kezelés</span>
          <h1 class="mt-5 text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tightest text-balance leading-[1.02]">
            Egy mosó? Öt szalon?<br/>
            <span class="grad-text-strong">Mindkettő otthon van.</span>
          </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 fade-up" style="transition-delay: 80ms">
          <p class="text-ink-600 text-lg text-pretty">
            Egyetlen szalonnal indulsz, később pedig ugyanaz a rendszer kezeli az egész lánc 5–6 telephelyét — <b class="text-ink-900">közös admin</b>, közös vendég-bázis, lánc-szintű hűségpont és bérlet, szalon-szintű árazás.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-6 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 fade-up space-y-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-leaf-50 ring-1 ring-leaf-200 p-6">
            <div class="grid place-items-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-white text-leaf-700 ring-1 ring-leaf-200"><i data-lucide="building" class="w-5 h-5"></i></div>
            <h3 class="mt-3 font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2">Több telephely egy adminban</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">Szalon-választó az oldalsávban, vagy „Összes szalon” összesítő nézet — bevétellel, foglalásszámmal, kihasználtsággal.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-cyan-50 ring-1 ring-cyan-200 p-6">
            <div class="grid place-items-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-white text-cyan-700 ring-1 ring-cyan-200"><i data-lucide="users-round" class="w-5 h-5"></i></div>
            <h3 class="mt-3 font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2">Munkatárs több szalonhoz</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">Egy kolléga több telephelyen is dolgozhat. A naptár az aktuális szalon nézetét mutatja, a saját Google Naptárba minden szalonból bemennek a saját foglalások.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-ink-900 text-white p-6 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute -bottom-12 -right-12 w-32 h-32 grad-bg rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-30"></div>
            <div class="relative">
              <div class="grid place-items-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-white/10 text-leaf-400 ring-1 ring-white/15"><i data-lucide="gift" class="w-5 h-5"></i></div>
              <h3 class="mt-3 font-bold tracking-tighter2">Lánc-szintű hűség &amp; bérlet</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-white/70 leading-relaxed">A vendég bármelyik szalonban gyűjt és vált pontot. Konfigurálható: lánc-szintű (közös) vagy szalon-szintű elszámolás.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-lime-50 ring-1 ring-lime-200 p-6">
            <div class="grid place-items-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-white text-lime-700 ring-1 ring-lime-200"><i data-lucide="chart-line" class="w-5 h-5"></i></div>
            <h3 class="mt-3 font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2">Összevont kimutatás</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">Lánc-szintű bevétel-trend, szalon-szintű bontás, kolléga-rangsor szalonok között — egy export, egy CSV.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-3 fade-up" style="transition-delay: 100ms">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -inset-6 grad-bg blur-3xl opacity-15 rounded-[2rem]"></div>
            <div class="relative rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-ink-200 shadow-[0_40px_100px_-30px_rgba(9,9,11,0.25)] overflow-hidden">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 px-4 py-3 border-b border-ink-100 bg-ink-50">
                <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-ink-200"></span>
                <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-ink-200"></span>
                <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-ink-200"></span>
                <div class="ml-3 flex-1 h-6 rounded-md bg-white ring-1 ring-ink-200 px-2.5 text-[11px] text-ink-500 flex items-center gap-1.5">
                  <i data-lucide="lock" class="w-3 h-3"></i>
                  admin.te-lancod.hu / szalonok
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-5 lg:p-6">
                <div class="rounded-xl bg-ink-900 text-white p-5 relative overflow-hidden">
                  <div class="absolute -top-16 -right-16 w-48 h-48 grad-bg rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-35"></div>
                  <div class="relative flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
                    <div>
                      <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/55 font-bold">Lánc összesítve</div>
                      <div class="text-base font-extrabold tracking-tighter2">Te-Lánc Kft. · ma</div>
                    </div>
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-white/10 text-white text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase ring-1 ring-white/15 px-2 py-0.5">LIVE</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="relative grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3">
                    <div><div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/55 font-bold">Szalon</div><div class="text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tightest mt-0.5">5</div></div>
                    <div><div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/55 font-bold">Mosó</div><div class="text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tightest mt-0.5">18</div></div>
                    <div><div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/55 font-bold">Mai bevétel</div><div class="text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tightest mt-0.5">142e <span class="text-xs text-white/60 font-bold">Ft</span></div></div>
                    <div><div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/55 font-bold">Foglalás</div><div class="text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tightest mt-0.5">56</div></div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-5">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                    <div class="text-sm font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2">Szalonok</div>
                    <button class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest text-ink-700 uppercase rounded-md ring-1 ring-ink-200 px-2 py-1"><i data-lucide="plus" class="w-3 h-3"></i> Új</button>
                  </div>
                  <ul class="space-y-2 text-xs">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl bg-leaf-50 ring-1 ring-leaf-200 px-3.5 py-3 relative overflow-hidden">
                      <span class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 grad-bg"></span>
                      <span class="grid place-items-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl grad-bg text-ink-900 text-xs font-extrabold">B1</span>
                      <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                        <div class="font-bold text-ink-900 truncate flex items-center gap-1.5">Belváros <span class="text-[9px] font-bold tracking-widest grad-bg text-ink-900 rounded-full px-1.5 py-0.5">CSÚCS</span></div>
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-ink-500 truncate">Budapest V. · 4 mosó · Szabó G., Nagy A.</div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="text-right shrink-0">
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-ink-500 font-semibold">Ma</div>
                        <div class="font-extrabold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2">38e Ft · 14</div>
                      </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl bg-cyan-50 ring-1 ring-cyan-200 px-3.5 py-3">
                      <span class="grid place-items-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-ink-900 text-white text-xs font-extrabold">B2</span>
                      <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                        <div class="font-bold text-ink-900 truncate">Budafok</div>
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-ink-500 truncate">Budapest XXII. · 3 mosó · Kis V.</div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="text-right shrink-0">
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-ink-500 font-semibold">Ma</div>
                        <div class="font-extrabold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2">22e Ft · 8</div>
                      </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl bg-lime-50 ring-1 ring-lime-200 px-3.5 py-3">
                      <span class="grid place-items-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-ink-900 text-white text-xs font-extrabold">V</span>
                      <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                        <div class="font-bold text-ink-900 truncate">Veresegyház</div>
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-ink-500 truncate">Pest · 4 mosó · Tóth J., Pap E.</div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="text-right shrink-0">
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-ink-500 font-semibold">Ma</div>
                        <div class="font-extrabold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2">31e Ft · 12</div>
                      </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl bg-leaf-50 ring-1 ring-leaf-200 px-3.5 py-3">
                      <span class="grid place-items-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-ink-900 text-white text-xs font-extrabold">D</span>
                      <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                        <div class="font-bold text-ink-900 truncate">Debrecen</div>
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-ink-500 truncate">Hajdú-Bihar · 5 mosó · 3 munkatárs</div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="text-right shrink-0">
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-ink-500 font-semibold">Ma</div>
                        <div class="font-extrabold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2">41e Ft · 18</div>
                      </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl bg-cyan-50 ring-1 ring-cyan-200 px-3.5 py-3">
                      <span class="grid place-items-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-ink-900 text-white text-xs font-extrabold">SZ</span>
                      <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                        <div class="font-bold text-ink-900 truncate">Szeged</div>
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-ink-500 truncate">Csongrád · 2 mosó · Varga M.</div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="text-right shrink-0">
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-ink-500 font-semibold">Ma</div>
                        <div class="font-extrabold text-ink-900 tracking-tighter2">10e Ft · 4</div>
                      </div>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-5 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                  <div class="rounded-xl bg-ink-50 ring-1 ring-ink-200 p-3.5">
                    <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-500 font-bold">Heti trend</div>
                    <div class="mt-1 flex items-baseline gap-1.5">
                      <span class="text-lg font-extrabold tracking-tightest text-ink-900">+18%</span>
                      <span class="text-[10px] text-leaf-700 font-bold">▲</span>
                    </div>
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 120 28" class="mt-1 w-full" preserveAspectRatio="none">
                      <path d="M0 22 L15 18 L30 20 L45 14 L60 16 L75 10 L90 12 L105 6 L120 8" fill="none" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div class="rounded-xl bg-ink-50 ring-1 ring-ink-200 p-3.5">
                    <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-500 font-bold">Várható havi</div>
                    <div class="mt-1 flex items-baseline gap-1.5">
                      <span class="text-lg font-extrabold tracking-tightest text-ink-900">12.8 M Ft</span>
                    </div>
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 120 28" class="mt-1 w-full" preserveAspectRatio="none">
                      <path d="M0 22 L20 18 L40 20 L60 14 L80 10 L100 8 L120 4" fill="none" stroke="#06b6d4" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="3 2"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 rounded-2xl bg-ink-900 text-white p-6 lg:p-7 relative overflow-hidden fade-up">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-30" style="background-image: radial-gradient(at 0% 50%, rgba(132,204,22,0.35), transparent 50%), radial-gradient(at 100% 50%, rgba(6,182,212,0.30), transparent 50%);"></div>
        <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="grid place-items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl grad-bg text-ink-900 shrink-0"><i data-lucide="building-2" class="w-6 h-6"></i></div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-[11px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-widest text-leaf-400">Lánc-pricing</div>
              <h3 class="mt-1 text-xl lg:text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter2">Per szalon <span class="grad-text">9 900 Ft / hó</span> — központi admin ingyenes.</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-white/70">5 szalon = 49 500 Ft / hó. Vendég, foglalás, mosó, szolgáltatás minden szalonban korlátlan.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="#" data-contact-source="NETWORK_QUOTE" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full grad-bg text-ink-900 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold shrink-0 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-transform">
            Ajánlatkérés
            <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
